http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/FromButton
Server
Returns true during a function added with {{LibraryFunction| numpad|Register}}

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/OnDown Server Adds a function to call when a player presses a key on the number pad
Player ply: The player whose numpad should be watched
number key: The key, corresponding to {{Enum|KEY}}
string name: The name of the function to run, corresponding with the one used in {{LibraryFunction|numpad|Register}}
any args: Arguments to pass to the function

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/OnUp Server Adds a function to call when a player releases a key on the number pad
Player ply: The player whose numpad should be watched
number key: The key, corresponding to {{Enum|KEY}}
string name: The name of the function to run, corresponding with the one used in {{LibraryFunction|numpad|Register}}
any ...: Arguments to pass to the function

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/Register Server Registers a numpad library action for use with {{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnDown}} and {{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnUp}}
string id: The unique id of your action.
function func: The function to be executed.

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/Remove
Server
Removes a function added by either {{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnUp}} or
{{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnDown}}

string name: The name added via {{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnUp}} or {{LibraryFunction|numpad|OnDown}}

http://wiki.garrysmod.com/page/numpad/Toggle Server Either runs {{LibraryFunction|numpad|Activate}} or {{LibraryFunction|numpad|Deactivate}} depending on the key's current state
Player ply: The player whose numpad should be simulated
number key: The key to press, corresponding to {{Enum|KEY}}

